comment.text: This key provides the placeholder text for an input field prompting the user to enter a name. It appears in dialogs related to AI settings, specifically for adding or updating AI providers and managing server headers. Translators should ensure the wording is clear and concise for entering a user-defined title or name.

usage.context:
<TextInput
 type={InputType.text}
 size={InputSize.base}
 value={headerNames[index]}
 onChange={(e) => onChangeHeaderName(index, e.target.value)}
 placeholder={t("AISettings:EnterLabel")}
 scale
 />
 </FieldContainer>
 <FieldContainer
 labelText={t("AISettings:HeaderValue")}
